# what is git

So, what is Git in a nutshell? This is an important section to absorb,
because if you understand what Git is and the fundamentals of how it works,
then using Git effectively will probably be much easier for you.

1. *Git* is distrbuted version control
2. used on computer *local machine*
3. multy *devs* contibute  on same project

## What is the Version Control?

Version Control is a system that allows you to revisit 
various versions of a file or set of files by recording changes.

